# QA & Chat UI Verification Walkthrough

## Phase 1: 11-Step Flow QA Audit

Performed a line-by-line audit of the entire data flow from [CreateRagModal.jsx](file:///c:/Users/e629/Documents/AgenticRag/chatbotui/src/components/CreateRagModal.jsx) → [main.py](file:///c:/Users/e629/Documents/AgenticRag/backend/main.py) → [haystack_service.py](file:///c:/Users/e629/Documents/AgenticRag/backend/services/haystack_service.py) → specialized pipeline modules.

### Findings

| Step | Area | Status | Notes |
|------|------|--------|-------|
| 1-2 | Data Input | ✔ Pass | `scrapeMode` correctly routes to static (BS4) or dynamic (Playwright). File uploads append parsed text via `/api/upload`. |
| 3 | DB Selection | ✔ Pass | [create_document_store](file:///c:/Users/e629/Documents/AgenticRag/backend/services/vector_store_manager.py#248-311) routes Cloud/Local/Hybrid with API key passthrough from `config.apiKeys`. |
| 4-5 | Architecture + Dynamic Config | ✔ Pass | All 5 specialized modules (voice, crosslingual, conversational, agentic, graph) consume `dynamicConfig`. Standard types use [_get_prompt_template](file:///c:/Users/e629/Documents/AgenticRag/backend/services/haystack_service.py#38-121). |
| 6 | Models | ✔ Pass | [get_generator](file:///c:/Users/e629/Documents/AgenticRag/backend/services/llm_service.py#209-233) factory correctly maps all model IDs with API key fallbacks. |
| 7 | Tuning | ✔ Pass | `chunkSize` → `DocumentSplitter`, `topK` → `InMemoryBM25Retriever`, `useReranker` → `TransformersSimilarityRanker`. |
| 8 | Features | ✔ Pass | `privacyMode`, `explainability`, and `features[]` all inject into prompt templates. |

**No frontend-to-backend misalignments were found.**

