## Phase 2: StandaloneChat UI Rebuild

Completely rebuilt [StandaloneChat.jsx](file:///c:/Users/e629/Documents/AgenticRag/chatbotui/src/StandaloneChat.jsx) with:

- **Markdown-lite rendering** — Bold text, inline code, and `[1]` citation superscripts
- **Voice input** — MediaRecorder API with mic toggle button
- **TTS audio playback** — Play button for voice pipeline responses
- **Pipeline metadata header** — Shows LLM model, DB type, doc count, and LIVE indicator
- **Copy-to-clipboard** — Hover action on bot messages
- **Backend fix** — Updated `/api/visualize` in [main.py](file:///c:/Users/e629/Documents/AgenticRag/backend/main.py) to return `pipeline_metadata` alongside graph data

